>[Question]
>Sam’s favorite colors are blue and green, so it’s not surprising 
>that he has six blue sox and six green sox in his sock drawer. 
>Unfortunately, they are hopelessly mixed up and one day, in complete 
>darkness, he has to grab some sox to wear. How many sox does he have 
>to take from the drawer to make sure he gets a matching pair—either 
>green or blue?
