Hi Stacey,

thanks for writing to the Math Forum.

Suppose he picks two socks.  Either they're both blue (in which case
he's done) or they're both green (in which case he's done), or
he's got one of each (so he needs to pick another sock).

What can happen when he picks the next sock?

